snippet.title: Temporal Purge: Z - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Become an interdimensional zombie slayer in Temporal Purge: Z, an action-packed zombie-survival FPS. Face the zombie onslaught as you eradicate countless undead monsters on your quest to save the future. 

Get the demo for free on Steam right now!
